{
  "stem": "14002.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Whoever-- whoever had something-- something to say about a kapo-- and most of them were bad-- they never got out alive there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I have seen, myself, where they killed a Polish kapo.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Then they got a hold on that kapo, what I mentioned before, they got a hold of him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But he-- I was outside of the barrack at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "For some reason or another, he tore himself out from there and he ran out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He jumped out-- he jumped out-- out of the-- of the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And there was that-- the German guard, that civilian guard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That civilian guard told him, halt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And this kapo hollered, ich-- ich bin ein Deutscher.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So the German guard told him, macht schnell.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "That was the last I saw of him, of that guard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Anyway, the Americans came in, over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I don't think that they knew what they were doing either.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They didn't realize what-- what they are dealing with, who they are dealing with.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They started to give food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Whoever could go for that food, they got sick right away afterwards.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Then the next day, they took some town people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "They took all those dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "The town people had to take all those dead bodies and put it on wagons and take it out somewhere to burn them or to bury them, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then, a few days later, everybody had to register where he's from.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Of course, I registered I'm from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "It was a rainy day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "It came a-- a truck, an open truck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "They took us in the open truck, whoever was going to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "They put us in the open truck, with the rain and everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
